title.en: Kao ga Miwakerarenai Hakushaku Reijou Desu ga, Akunin Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai Sarete Imasu
Senjou no Seijo ~Imouto no Kawari ni Koushaku Kishi ni Totsugu Koto ni narimashita ga, Ima wa Shiawase desu~
Kinou made Namae mo Yonde Kurenakatta Koushaku-sama ga, Kyuu ni Dekiai shitekuru no desu ga?
Maryoku ga nai to Kandousaremashita ga, Oukyuu de Seijou Hajimemasu
Konyaku Hakisareta Gakeppuchi Reijou wa, Teikoku no Sumeragi Otouto Denka to Musubareru
Batsu 3 no Mitori Fujin to Yobareteimasu no de Suteoite Kudasaimase
Kore kara Shiawase ni narimasu! Shiitagerare Reijou desu ga Tekitaikoku no Koushaku-sama ni Naze ka Dekiaisaretemasu
Oguni no Koushaku Reijou wa Tekikoku nite Kakusei suru
Imouto ni Konyakusha wo Toraretara Mishiranu Koushaku-sama ni Kyuukonsaremashita
"Omae ga Kawari ni Shine" to Iwareta Watashi. Imouto no Migawari ni Reikoku na Henkyou Haku no Moto e Totsugi, Shiawase wo Teniireru
"Shinde Miro" to Iwareta no de Shinimashita
Kokurou Ou to Shirogane no Niehime
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
Nariyuki de Konyaku wo Moushikonda Yowaki Binbou Reijou desuga, Nazeka Jiki Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai sarete Torawarete imasu
